## Bug 3: Program name not sent to Airtable

**Priority**: HIGH | **Status**: FIXED

### Root Cause
`upsertProgram()` in `api/_lib/sync/airtable-writers.ts` was missing the `name` field when writing program data to Airtable via the outbox sync worker. The program name was saved correctly in Postgres but never synced to Airtable.

### Fix Applied
Added `name` field mapping to `upsertProgram()`:
```typescript
if (payload.name) {
  fields[PROGRAM_FIELDS.name] = payload.name
}
```

### Files Changed
- `api/_lib/sync/airtable-writers.ts` - Added `name` field to `upsertProgram()`

