## Related: Goede Gewoontes Feature (Uncommitted)

Not reported as a UAT bug, but discovered during investigation: the Goede Gewoontes onboarding chain was broken. The feature was fully implemented on the backend but not wired through the frontend wizard.

### Issues Found and Fixed
1. `api/programs/preview.ts` didn't pass `goedeGewoontes` to AI `buildSystemPrompt` - AI couldn't select habits
2. `api/programs/preview.ts` didn't return `suggestedGoedeGewoontes` in response
3. Wizard `AIPreviewResult` type missing `suggestedGoedeGewoontes`
4. `handleConfirm` in wizard didn't pass `selectedGoedeGewoontes` to confirm endpoint
5. `ProgramResult.tsx` didn't display AI-selected goede gewoontes

### Fix Applied
- Backend: Preview endpoint now passes goede gewoontes to AI and returns selections
- Frontend types: Added `suggestedGoedeGewoontes` to preview result, `selectedGoedeGewoontes` to generate result
- Frontend wizard: `handleConfirm` maps and passes goede gewoontes to confirm
- Frontend display: ProgramResult shows goede gewoontes with name + AI reason
- i18n: Added `goedeGewoontes.title` translations (nl/fr/en)

### Files Changed
- `api/programs/preview.ts`
- `src/types/program.ts`
- `src/components/AIProgramWizard/types.ts`
- `src/components/AIProgramWizard/index.tsx`
- `src/components/AIProgramWizard/ProgramResult.tsx`
- `src/lib/i18n-fallback.ts`

